Package co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence

Class DataMapper

java.lang.Object
co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence.DataMapper
public class DataMapper extends Object
The DataMapper class provides utility methods to convert between Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) and their corresponding entity classes for various product types such as Pincel, Pintura, and ProyectoMadera. This facilitates the transformation of data between different layers of the application, ensuring separation of concerns and ease of data manipulation.

This class contains static methods and is not meant to be instantiated.
